---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
import Compass from "../assets/compass.jpg";
import Cta from "@components/cta.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Meet the founders of The Financial Helm. A modern accountancy practice built by an expert accountant and technology specialist to close the gap between numbers and operations."
  footerMargin={false}
>
  <Container class="mt-16">
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">We Believe Your Finance Function Should Be Your Strongest Asset, Not Your Biggest
        Bottleneck
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-content-primary">
            The Financial Helm was founded on a simple observation: most growing businesses are held back by a critical
            gap between their accounting and their day-to-day operations. The numbers are handled by one person, the
            systems by another, and the founder is left trying to bridge the divide.
          </p>
          <p class="text-content-primary font-bold mt-4">
            We exist to close that gap for good.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>
  </Container>

  <div class="bg-surface-secondary py-16 my-16">
    <Container>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mx-auto">
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute hidden md:block w-96 h-96 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full right-0 top-1/3 -z-10">
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute hidden md:block w-44 h-44 bg-brand-navy/10 rounded-full left-10 top-1/4 -z-10">
          </div>
          <Picture
            formats={["avif", "webp"]}
            src={Compass}
            alt="Marine compass on boat dashboard with sunlit water in background"
            layout="constrained"
            class="rounded-xl w-full max-w-md mx-auto shadow-2xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="place-self-center">
          <h2 class="text-5xl text-content-primary tracking-tight -mt-2">
            Two Perspectives, One Solution
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg max-w-xl mt-4 leading-relaxed text-content-secondary">
            For years, from two different professional worlds, we saw the same problem from opposite sides.
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-content-primary text-lg font-bold mt-6 text-left">The Accountant's View</h2>
          <p class="max-w-xl mt-2 leading-relaxed text-content-secondary">
            As an expert accountant, Emma saw the consequences of broken systems every day. She worked with ambitious
            founders who had brilliant products and impressive growth, but whose financial operations were held together
            by fragile spreadsheets, manual data entry, and sheer willpower. This "creeping chaos" led to delayed
            decisions, unclear profitability, and founders who were trapped working in their business, not on it.
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-content-primary text-lg font-bold mt-6 text-left">The Technologist's View</h2>
          <p class="max-w-xl mt-2 leading-relaxed text-content-secondary">
            As a tech automation specialist, Stuart saw the other side of the coin. He saw powerful, accessible
            technology
            that could eliminate these bottlenecks, but it was often poorly implemented or completely overlooked by
            traditional finance professionals. The potential for efficiency was huge, but it required a systems-thinking
            mindset that most accountants simply didn't have.
          </p>
          <p class="max-w-xl mt-2 leading-relaxed text-content-secondary">
            <b>The Financial Helm was born when we realised the solution wasn't just better accounting or smarter
              techâ€”it
              was
              the seamless integration of both.</b> We built a new kind of accountancy practice, one that architects the
            operational engine that powers our clients' growth.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </div>

  <Container class="pb-16">
    <div class="mt-24 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl lg:tracking-tight text-center text-content-primary">
        Meet the Founders
      </h2>
      <h2 class="text-content-primary text-lg font-bold mt-8 text-left">Emma James | Co-Founder</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-content-secondary">
        Emma is the accountant and financial strategist. With over 10 years of experience, she ensures every system we
        build is rooted in robust, compliant accounting principles. Her aim is to empower founders, by transforming
        financial data from a historical record into a powerful tool for real-time, forward-looking decision-making. She
        is the architect of your financial clarity.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-content-primary text-lg font-bold mt-8 text-left">Stuart Chapman | Co-Founder</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-content-secondary">
        Stuart is the systems specialist. He translates complex operational challenges into elegant, automated
        workflows. With a background in software development, having worked with The University of Cambridge and The
        Economist, amongst others, he ensures that the technology we implement is perfectly tailored to streamline and
        automate your processes. He is the engineer of your financial efficiency.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl lg:tracking-tight text-center text-content-primary">
        Our Mission is Simple
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mt-6 leading-relaxed text-content-primary font-bold">
        To move business owners from being a bottleneck in their finances to being in control of them.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-content-primary">
        We replace outdated, manual processes with streamlined systems that provide clarity, eliminate operational drag,
        and free up ambitious leaders to focus on what they do best: scaling their company.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
  <Cta />
</Layout>
